# AIdrafter WordPress Plugin

AIdrafter is a WordPress plugin that uses the OpenAI API to generate unique content for your blog. It works by using a neural network to complete a given prompt.

## Installation

To install the plugin, simply download the latest release from the [releases page](https://github.com/your-username/aidrafter/releases) and extract the contents to your `wp-content/plugins` directory. Then, activate the plugin from the WordPress Dashboard.

You will also need an API key from OpenAI to use this plugin.

## Usage

Once the plugin is installed and activated, you can create a new post as usual. In the post editor, you will see a new section labeled "AIdrafter" where you can enter a prompt for the neural network. 

After you publish the post, the plugin will automatically generate content for your post based on the prompt you provided.

